                                    <input name="CheckTerms" value="true" type="radio" id="checkTerms" onclick="return false;" />
                                    <span><i></i><a href="javascript:showHealthyTerms();" class="col-red"><u>課前健康狀況自我檢視聲明書</u></a></span>
